metadata.name: Divine Moments of Trump; DMT
metadata.description: In fall 2017, I smoked DMT while on psilocybin and experienced a very specific detailed vision. Upon breaking through, I saw Donald Trump smoking DMT from a pipe wearing a tribal patterned hippie-type shirt. It then progressed to him leading other ignorant folks through the amazon on a quest to do ayahuasca. They got to the circle with the shaman and they ingested ayahuasca. There was a Trump attitude about drinking it, “MORE!!! BIGGER DOSES!!” They purged and purged and the earth began to heal. Earth began to speak to me and said, “Don’t worry, there is enough medicine here to heal our most toxic parts.” As if him and the others are toxic shadow traits of a bigger whole being. That there is no separation between me and these world leaders, and no doubt that we are one. There was a deep knowing of the healing potential that exists. After that my organs began to be lined with gold and I was healing in ways unimaginable while an angel was a witness over my shoulder.
